schools.name: The Academies at Jonesboro High School

data.description: Welcome to market, central location, maintenance free living, with fenced back yard for family gatherings or entertaining. Conveniently located, all of Jonesboro Arkansas is at your fingertips, 2 bedroom & 1 bath, recently remodeled with upgrades to kitchen appliances. Eat in kitchen and abundant storage in the oversized laundry room. Large living room with refurbished hardwood flooring in LR, bedroom, and hallway. Main bedroom has 2 closets. Large shady back yard fenced with chain link. Only 3 blocks from Jonesboro high school. Great starter home or investment property. Priced to sell.
